comments: Interesting task, although time between words showing was very small meaning often didn't grasp whole sentence

I found it quite difficult to follow the long sentences! Sometimes I'd think later about how I'd got the previous sentence wrong, because I needed more time to process the sentence than the task would allow me!
It was hard to know whether you were looking for purely grammatical errors or also errors in sentence meaning.
I enjoyed the challenge given the speed of which the sentences appeared.

Unsure why the words had to appear one at a time, they flew by so fast. Some of the sentences, while technically correct, made no sense. The 3 second time limit to choose an answer seemed fairly tight.
I would probably change up the background colour as the task goes on as the glaring white can make your eyes go funny after a while.
